name: Cornell Pro-Yos
desc: I’m a member of a Chinese Yoyo performance group known as the Pro-Yos! We perform at several events each semester, culminating in a big showcase performance at the end of the spring semester. I also served as the club’s secretary for one semester.

name: Engineering Ambassadors
desc: I am part of Cornell’s Engineering Ambassadors, where I am responsible for giving tours for prospective and newly admitted students to the college of engineering as well as hosting Q&A sessions.
